{"tid":1689283,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"今次要幫消防手，下次唔會有人企出黎！","createTime":"2019-11-02T17:41:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T18:40:38.000Z","uid":19055,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"dc8b1fbb9905ec0c092baf9b15b0dbd6b0b998f9","tid":1689283,"uid":19055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:41:05.000Z","msg":"今日有消防員比popo推撞，有傳返局已被高層照肺，請幫手電郵去表揚消防<br />\n<br />\n[url]dfs@hkfsd.gov.hk[/url]<br />\n[url]hkfsdenq@hkfsd.gov.hk[/url]<br />\n[url]ceo@ceo.gov.hk[/url]<br />\n<br />\n讚揚消防處人員及建議消防處暫停配合警方於公眾活動中執勤以保障消防處人員人身安全<br />\n<br />\n在11月2日的公眾活動，消防處人員一如既往為市民提供緊急救援服務，本人特此讚揚消防處人員的付出。<br />\n<br />\n但是，本人同時留意到消防處人員在十分危險的環境下工作，於11月2日兩度受彈藥攻擊以及被警察毆打。在片段一中，消防處人員在沒有任何裝備的情況下被警察以催淚彈攻擊，在下車避險時更被警察毆打。在片段二中，消防處人員更被警察以實彈攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n一直以來，無論在山上拯救被困人士(有消防員更曾為警察殉職)及火場中，消防處人員在承受極人風險的情況下工作，但現時消防處人員執勤竟被針對，以實彈攻擊及毆打，如此惡劣工作環境實在太荒謬。建議消防處暫停配合警方於公眾活動中執勤以保障消防處人員人身安全。<br />\n<br />\n片段一<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TaJ3QSyi_aU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTaJ3QSyi_aU&d=5AUjfk%2BhgFT%2FKzSacqcGpIc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=2f2481ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TaJ3QSyi_aU</a><br />\n片段二<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/groups/803879953032830/permalink/2552993321454809\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F803879953032830%2Fpermalink%2F2552993321454809&d=5AUjfk%2BhgFT%2FKzSacqcGpIc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=688da6ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/groups/803879953032830/permalink/2552993321454809</a>"},{"pid":"ae48ec81c03f2a7d163359683d245f24e55de9a2","tid":1689283,"uid":262146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:41:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/daWoJsy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdaWoJsy.png&h=16518c90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oLQwSkW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoLQwSkW.png&h=766c26b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TLR4sUj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTLR4sUj.png&h=1dd0aacc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n死黑警從來無認真關心過香港人條命<br />\n講緊被死亡個案，佢仲係度冷笑、當笑話"},{"pid":"fe17c6a243216c93ce706e0a706c2d804599b6d7","tid":1689283,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:42:14.000Z","msg":"有心幫唔好一式一樣，花多少少時間自己打封信，甚至打電話去感謝人"},{"pid":"1840dcc04771b3594d9bce25263becf1624c41cc","tid":1689283,"uid":19055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:42:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88c12573b53fbe8c55256ae56dd169eae13af4e6","tid":1689283,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:43:14.000Z","msg":"TUI"},{"pid":"3bdb924677386ae706addb1785e558271e9db770","tid":1689283,"uid":19055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:43:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8c5574491ded49c1d05ca9bd65578e2086de9fd","tid":1689283,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:43:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ee8ddac54ae364037fa62d1cb6821746dd62b4f6","tid":1689283,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:43:56.000Z","msg":"支持消防員集會"},{"pid":"d2e730c8aa241e46f1938121bc3338d7bd06b986","tid":1689283,"uid":19055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:44:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e06488f57fa5e906129775128985905168cb411","tid":1689283,"uid":312125,"like